Reasoning: The paper discusses extending distributional semantics beyond individual words, which is a topic that falls under the subfield of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of supervised learning to generate combination functions also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also evaluates its approach on tasks related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CC).
